            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Cassius <lb n="2"/>Secundus <lb n="3"/>|(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>donis <expan><abbr>donat</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>corona mura<supplied reason="lost">li</supplied> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>phaler</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>torquib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>armillis <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>arbitr</abbr><ex>atu</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Saxi Primi <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ocus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>epulturae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei nicht aneinander passende Fragmente erhalten. Abmessungen des oberen Fragments: s. o.; Abmessungen des unteren Fragments: (66) x (120). Rekonstruierbare Maße nach Karl: ca. 148.5 x 125 cm. Material: Bacherer Marmor. Fundjahr: zwischen 1826 und 1831 in der zweiten Abbruchphase des Alten Turms.</p>
            </div>
